"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiE~aAlN", "text_ar": "فِعَّالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Mgh, Msb,) from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ab~ana", "text_ar": "اَبَّنَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "“he watched” or “observed” a thing, (Mgh,) the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "n", "text_ar": "ن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "being radical: (Msb:) but the former derivation is the more correct. (Mgh.) [See also art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Abn", "text_ar": "ابن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]"}], "source_refs": ["Msb", "Mgh"]}, {"entry_id": "n103", "headword_ar": "اـِبَّانٌ", "root": "Abn", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "time"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a thing; (T, S, M, K, and Msb in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ab", "text_ar": "اب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "season"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a thing; (Msb in that art.;) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "time of the preparing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "making ready,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a thing; (Mgh in that art.;) as, for instance, of fruit, (S, Mgh, Msb,) of the fresh ripe dates, and of the gathering of fruits, and of heat or cold: (T.:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "first"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a thing. (M, K.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^axa*a Al$~aYo'a biA_ib~aAnihi", "text_ar": "اَخَذَ الشَّىْءَ بِاـِبَّانِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He took the thing in its time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with, the first thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M.) The"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "n", "text_ar": "ن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is radical, so that it is of the measure"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiE~aAlN", "text_ar": "فِعَّالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; or, as some say, augmentative, so that it is of the measure"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiEolaAnN", "text_ar": "فِعْلَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) [See art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ab", "text_ar": "اب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "Msb"]}, {"entry_id": "n3662", "headword_ar": "ابان", "root": "byn", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", intrans., inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ibaAnapN", "text_ar": "اـِبَانَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": see 1, in two places.       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAnhu", "text_ar": "ابانهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (inf. n. as above, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He separated it, severed it, disunited it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "cut it off."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, Msb, K, TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Darabahu faA^abaAna raA^osahu", "text_ar": "ضَرَبَهُ فَاَبَانَ رَاْسَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He smote him and severed his head,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino", "text_ar": "مِنْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jasadihi", "text_ar": "جَسَدِهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from his body."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn AlmaroA^apa", "text_ar": "ابان المَرْاَةَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(the husband)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "separated the woman,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wife,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by divorce. (Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn binotahu", "text_ar": "ابان بِنْتَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "by~nhA", "text_ar": "بيّنها", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T, K,) inf. n. of the former as above, and of the latter"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taboyiynN", "text_ar": "تَبْيِينٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He married,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gave in marriage, his daughter,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and she went to her husband:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T:) from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayonN", "text_ar": "بَيْنٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifying \"distance:\" as though he removed her to a distance from the house, or tent, of her mother. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn A@bonahu bimaAlK", "text_ar": "ابان ا@بْنَهُ بِمَالٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAnhu A^abawaAhu", "text_ar": "ابانهُ اَبَوَاهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He separated from himself his son,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "his two parents separated him from themselves,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "giving him"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "property,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, M,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to be his alone:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T:) mentioned on the authority of AZ. (T, M.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn Ald~alowa Eano TiY~i Albiy^ori", "text_ar": "ابان الدَّلْوَ عَنْ طِىِّ البِيْرِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He drew away the bucket from the casing of the well, lest the latter should lacerate the former."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M.) ―         -b2-  See also 2, in three places. ―         -b3-  [Hence,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn", "text_ar": "ابان"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He spoke,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "wrote, perspicuously, clearly, plainly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distinctly, as to meaning;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with eloquence:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bayaAnN", "text_ar": "بَيَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", q. v.] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn Ealayohi", "text_ar": "ابان عَلَيْهِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He spoke perspicuously, clearly, plainly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distinctly, and gave his testimony,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "evidence,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "gave decisive information, against him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "respecting it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) [The verb thus used is for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AbAn kalaAmahu", "text_ar": "ابان كَلَامَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$ahaAdatahu", "text_ar": "شَهَادَتَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] One says of a drunken man,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA yubiynu kalaAmFA", "text_ar": "مَا يُبِينُ كَلَامًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He does not speak plainly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distinctly;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "lit.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "does not make speech plain,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "distinct."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ks, T in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bt", "text_ar": "بت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b4-  ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA A^aboyanahu", "text_ar": "مَا اَبْيَنَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "How distinct, apparent, manifest, evident, clear,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "plain, is it!"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "See an ex. voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "basula", "text_ar": "بَسُلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "t